				<description>&lt;p&gt;Mac使用mosh登录新的服务器，发现如下错误：&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;blockquote&#xA;    class=&#34;border-primary bg-muted/30 hover:bg-muted/40 my-6 rounded-r-lg border-l-4 py-4 pr-4 pl-6 italic transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:translate-x-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;prose prose-sm max-w-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;bash: warning: setlocale: LC_ALL: cannot change locale (en_US.UTF-8)&#xA;The locale requested by LC_ALL=en_US.UTF-8 isn&amp;rsquo;t available here.&#xA;Running `locale-gen en_US.UTF-8&amp;rsquo; may be necessary.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The locale requested by LC_ALL=en_US.UTF-8 isn&amp;rsquo;t available here.&#xA;Running `locale-gen en_US.UTF-8&amp;rsquo; may be necessary.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
