				<description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;怎么引用另外一个markdown文件&#34;&gt;怎么引用另外一个markdown文件&lt;a href=&#34;#%e6%80%8e%e4%b9%88%e5%bc%95%e7%94%a8%e5%8f%a6%e5%a4%96%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aamarkdown%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a&#xA;    href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/content-management/cross-references/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;https://gohugo.io/content-management/cross-references/&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;方法是是用 &lt;code&gt;shortcode&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Shortcodes for creating links to documents.&#xA;The ref and relref shortcodes display the absolute and relative permalinks to a document, respectively.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
